### ✅ Signup - teammate (nominal)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "alice",
  "password": "password123"
}

### ✅ Signup - teamlead (nominal)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "boby",
  "password": "password123",
  "role": "teamlead"
}

### ❌ Signup - tentative admin (doit retourner 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "hacker",
  "password": "password123",
  "role": "admin"
}

### ❌ Signup - mot de passe trop court (doit retourner 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "charlie",
  "password": "short"
}

### ❌ Signup - username déjà pris (doit retourner 409)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "alice",
  "password": "password123"
}

### ✅ Login - nominal (copiez le token dans @token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "alice",
  "password": "password123"
}

### ❌ Login - mauvais mot de passe (doit retourner 401)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "alice",
  "password": "wrongpassword"
}

### ❌ Login - utilisateur inexistant (doit retourner 401)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "nobody",
  "password": "password123"
}

### ✅ Me - utilisateur connecté
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ✅ Me - sans token (doit retourner user: null)
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me

### ✅ Logout
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
